title: Mind Erasure - Promo 2013
description:
Mind Erasure is a Blackened Death metal band from corfu greece. Main influences are Behemoth, Bolt Thrower, Impaled Nazarene,Hate,Bloodbath and Amon Amarth, they have played in few events, but have shared stage with bands such us Rotting Christ, Tardive Dyskenesia, Eden Demise, and Silent Rage.
